### **3. 形状操作**
```python
import numpy as np

arr = np.array([[1, 2, 3], [4, 5, 6]])
print("原数组形状:", arr.shape)  # (2, 3)

# reshape - 改变形状
reshaped = arr.reshape(3, 2)
print("reshape后:")
print(reshaped)
print("新形状:", reshaped.shape)  # (3, 2)

# flatten - 展平
flattened = arr.flatten()
print("\n展平后:", flattened)
print("新形状:", flattened.shape)  # (6,)

# transpose - 转置
transposed = arr.T
print("\n转置后:")
print(transposed)
print("新形状:", transposed.shape)  # (3, 2)

# concatenate - 连接
arr1 = np.array([[1, 2], [3, 4]])
arr2 = np.array([[5, 6], [7, 8]])
concatenated = np.concatenate([arr1, arr2], axis=0)
print("\n连接后:")
print(concatenated)
print("新形状:", concatenated.shape)  # (4, 2)
```

